data.name: AboutLabel.Text
data.value:
BKSMTool is an open-source C# application designed to help users modify and manage audio files contained within .bnk archives, which are typically generated by the Wwise audio engine.
The tool provides both a graphical user interface (GUI) and a command-line interface (CLI) to facilitate the extraction, playback, replacement, and conversion of audio files like .wem, .wav, .mp3, and .ogg.
Key Features: - List, extract, and convert .wem audio files from .bnk archives. - Replace audio files within .bnk files. - Supports various audio formats for extraction and replacement (WAV, MP3, OGG). - Provides a command-line interface for batch processing. - Optional automatic update checking. - BKSMTool is built using several external libraries, such as BASS for audio playback and ObjectListView for data visualization, and adheres to the open-source principles with licensing under the GNU General Public License (GPLv3).
